_sText:
Thanx for viewing, this is my first ever map created so go easy.
Comments and advice would be much appreciated. 
Map name came from a great friend of mine, sweeper. Enjoy guys

---HOW TO INSTALL GUIDE---
1) Download Link provided
2) Place the downloaded content into the following folder
3) C:/Program Files/Steam/steamapps/*steam username*/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps
4) Open Counter Strike Source and Get Crackin :D

Map made by KorvexX
Founder of Beyond Pixelz.
